(1, 'abacareers/2610', 'abacareers', 'рҹҢҠ Career Community: Team Wellness Activity\n\nA short career/community update for candidates and professionals who want to grow with better workplace habits.\n\nCareer / Community Details:\nвҖў ABA Human Resources team joined the HR Sunrise Fun Run.\nвҖў The activity focused on employee well-being, healthy lifestyle, and team spirit.\nвҖў A positive reminder that strong teams grow through shared energy and collaboration.\n\nMessage:\nвҖў Stay connected, keep learning, and continue building better career habits.\n\nрҹ”— Apply your CV to:\nTelegram: @seekfitjob\nEmail: hr@seekfitjob.com\nвҖ”вҖ”вҖ”вҖ”вҖ”вҖ”вҖ”вҖ”вҖ”вҖ”вҖ”вҖ”вҖ”вҖ”\nTG Channel: t.me/SeekFitJobKH\nMore jobs: www.seekfitjob.com', 1, '2026-07-08 15:36:20', 'career wellness'),
(2, 'channelcamupjob/11229', 'channelcamupjob', 'рҹҢҷ Career Wellness: Better Sleep Tips\n\nA short career/community update for candidates and professionals who want to grow with better workplace habits.\n\nCareer / Community Details:\nвҖў Good sleep supports stronger productivity and a calmer mindset.\nвҖў Keep a regular sleep and wake-up time.\nвҖў Reduce phone use before bed and avoid coffee after 3 PM.\nвҖў Create a cool, dark, and quiet room for better rest.\n\nMessage:\nвҖў Stay connected, keep learning, and continue building better career habits.\n\nрҹ”— Apply your CV to:\nTelegram: @seekfitjob\nEmail: hr@seekfitjob.com\nвҖ”вҖ”вҖ”вҖ”вҖ”вҖ”вҖ”вҖ”вҖ”вҖ”вҖ”вҖ”вҖ”вҖ”\nTG Channel: t.me/SeekFitJobKH\nMore jobs: www.seekfitjob.com', 1, '2026-07-08 15:36:20', 'banking job'),
