(212, 'chipmong/1509', 'chipmong', 'вҖјпёҸ Urgent Need for Supervisor, Database Administration вҖјпёҸ\n\nChip Mong Bank is on the lookout for a dynamic and experienced Supervisor, Database Administration who is ready to take charge of our database systems and drive innovation within our organization.\n\nрҹҡЁ Key Responsibilities:\nвң… System Development: Lead the development and enhancement of our current database systems to meet evolving business needs.\nвң… Monitoring & Management: Oversee in-house development, ensuring databases are running efficiently and securely while implementing best practices.\nвң… Performance Optimization: Analyze and optimize database performance, ensuring high availability and reliability of banking data.\nвң… Team Leadership: Mentor and guide a team of database administrators, fostering a collaborative and high-performance work environment.\nвң… Compliance & Security: Ensure all database operations comply with regulatory standards, safeguarding sensitive customer information.\n\nContact us  via Telegram: 067 563 563 (https://t.me/ChipMongBankHR)', 'https://t.me/chipmong/1509', '/public/images/chipmong/chipmong_1509.jpg', '2026-07-06 04:08:09', '2026-06-15 04:59:58'),
