(241, 'cdlhrjobs/8029', 'cdlhrjobs', 'рҹҡЁ Urgent Hiring | Digital Marketing Executive (Female Preferred)\n\nрҹ“Қ Working Hours: 9:00 AM вҖ“ 6:00 PM\nрҹ’° Salary: USD $400вҖ“$700/month (based on experience)\nрҹҺҒ Benefits: NSSF, Annual Leave, Annual Bonus, Paid Public Holidays, Leadership Training & Other Company Benefits\n\nWe\'re looking for someone who has:\nвң… 1вҖ“3 years of Digital Marketing/E-commerce experience (Fresh graduates with a strong portfolio are welcome)\nвң… Hands-on experience with Shopee, Lazada, TikTok & Facebook\nвң… Skills in content creation, reels, short videos & TikTok Live (preferred)\nвң… Good English communication skills\nвң… Creative, proactive, and able to work in a fast-paced environment\n\nрҹ“Ң Key Responsibilities:\nвҖў Manage digital marketing campaigns across multiple platforms\nвҖў Support e-commerce & social commerce activities\nвҖў Plan and coordinate TikTok Live & livestream sales\nвҖў Create engaging digital content\nвҖў Monitor campaign performance and collaborate with internal teams\n\nрҹ“© Apply now! \nThis is a very urgent opportunity for passionate digital marketing professionals looking to grow their careers.\n\nContact: (+855) 85334560 / (+855) 66406097 / (+855) 98224783\nCDL HR Telegram: https://t.me/cdlhrjob\nEmail: fb@cdl-consultant.com\n..............................\nвһӨTelegram Channel: t.me/cdlhrjobs\nвһӨ Website: eng.cdl-consultant.com\nвһӨ Facebook Page: https://www.facebook.com/CambodiaJobBoard\n..............................\nрқ—–рқ—ҝрқ—Ірқ—®рқҳҒрқ—¶рқҳғрқ—І рқ——рқ—¶рқ—®рқ—әрқ—јрқ—»рқ—ұ рқ—ҹрқ—¶рқ—»рқ—ёрқҳҖ рқ—–рқ—ј., рқ—ҹрқҳҒрқ—ұ (рқ—–рқ——рқ—ҹ-рқ—ӣрқ—Ҙ)\nбһҖбҹ’бһҡбһ»бһҳбһ бҹҠбһ»бһ“бһ”бҹ’бһҡбһ№бһҖбҹ’бһҹбһ¶бһҖбһ¶бһҡбһ„бһ¶бһҡбһҠбҹӮбһӣбһ‘бһ‘бһҪбһӣбһ”бһ¶бһ“бһҖбһ¶бһҡбһҮбһҝбһҮбһ¶бһҖбҹӢбһ–бһёбһўбһҸбһ·бһҗбһ·бһҮбһ“бһҸбһ¶бҹҶбһ„бһ–бһёбһҶбҹ’бһ“бһ¶бҹҶбҹўбҹ бҹЎбҹў', 'https://t.me/cdlhrjobs/8029', '', '2026-07-06 04:08:11', '2026-07-03 05:28:38'),
