(246, 'JTRBCareer/550', 'JTRBCareer', 'Job Opportunity with J Trust Royal Bank!\nWe are now seeking a potential candidate to fulfill the below position:\n- Web Application Manager https://bit.ly/4miH2ne\n- Relationship Credit Analyst https://bit.ly/3NxfTMC\n- Web Application https://bit.ly/4m9U5qG\n- Intern вҖ“ Personal Banker x3 https://bit.ly/499JiHO\n- Intern вҖ“ Personal Banker x1 Kompong Cham https://bit.ly/3DUZwrR\nDeadline: 01 June 2026\n\n- Senior Lending Manager https://bit.ly/42jed0r\n- Business Service Office https://bit.ly/4eRrnJP\nDeadline: 02 June 2026\n \nHOW TO APPLY:\nInterested candidate may apply through the above link or scan QR code, or via email address:  jtrjobs@jtrustroyal.com', 'https://t.me/JTRBCareer/550', '/public/images/JTRBCareer/JTRBCareer_550.jpg', '2026-07-06 04:08:12', '2026-05-19 10:14:42'),
(247, 'JTRBCareer/551', 'JTRBCareer', 'At J Trust Royal Bank, our people remained the center of our progress and the driving force behind every milestone we achieved. We believe that continuous learning and professional growth are essential to building future-ready talent and delivering exceptional customer experiences and sustainable growth.\n\nThatвҖҷs why we remain committed to investing in our employees through tailored development programs that empower them to grow, lead, and succeed at every stage of their career journey.\n \nOn May 18thвҖ“19th, 2026, we successfully hosted our \'TALENT CONNECT\' forum, specifically curated for our frontline professionals. This initiative was designed to bridge the gap between theory and real-world practice, empowering our next generation of bankers with the sharp insights needed to accelerate their goals and fast-track their career growth.', 'https://t.me/JTRBCareer/551', '/public/images/JTRBCareer/JTRBCareer_551.jpg', '2026-07-06 04:08:12', '2026-05-22 05:20:09'),
(248, 'JTRBCareer/560', 'JTRBCareer', 'Job Opportunity with J Trust Royal Bank!\nWe are now seeking a potential candidate to fulfill the below position:\n\n- вҒ Senior Personal Banker x1 Sihanouk Ville https://bit.ly/43o17zP\n- Personal Banker x1 Sihanouk Ville https://bit.ly/3S08Dyh\n- Customer Service Consultant x1 Phnom Penh https://bit.ly/4dzUgcn\n\nDeadline: 24 June 2026\n\nHOW TO APPLY:\nInterested candidate may apply through the above link or scan QR code, or via email address:  jtrjobs@jtrustroyal.com', 'https://t.me/JTRBCareer/560', '/public/images/JTRBCareer/JTRBCareer_560.jpg', '2026-07-06 04:08:12', '2026-06-12 02:55:24'),
