(250, 'JTRBCareer/562', 'JTRBCareer', 'Discover Your Path at J Trust Royal Bank\'s booth in Paragon University Careers Fair 2026!\nAre you ready to embark on an exciting journey in the banking sector?\n\nJoin us at J Trust Royal BankвҖҷs boot, where youвҖҷll learn more about your dream career opportunities and cutting-edge of bank products. \n\n- Date: Friday, 26th June 2026\n- Time: 9:00am-5:00pm \n- Venue: Paragon University Careers Fair 2026\n- Map: https://maps.app.goo.gl/qWHumUXphtDciNBH7\n\nYour dream career awaits! and collect your winnings!\nSee you soon! \n\n#SimplyBetterCareer #JTRBCareer', 'https://t.me/JTRBCareer/562', '/public/images/JTRBCareer/JTRBCareer_562.jpg', '2026-07-06 04:08:12', '2026-06-24 03:03:14'),
(251, 'JTRBCareer/563', 'JTRBCareer', 'J Trust Royal Bank participated in the Paragon University Career Fair on 26 June 2026, with an engaging booth full of activities. We shared insights about our culture, career paths, and current opportunities, connecting with attendees through interactive sessions and one-on-one conversations.\n\nWe truly appreciated the enthusiasm of everyone who stopped by. Thank you for making the event a success-we look forward to welcoming new talents and building future collaborations.', 'https://t.me/JTRBCareer/563', '/public/images/JTRBCareer/JTRBCareer_563.jpg', '2026-07-06 04:08:12', '2026-07-02 03:30:33'),
(252, 'JTRBCareer/567', 'JTRBCareer', 'Job Opportunity with J Trust Royal Bank!\nWe are now seeking a potential candidate to fulfill the below position:\n- Relationship Manager, Corporate Banking x2 https://bit.ly/4fiy1Yf\n- Relationship Manager, SME Lending in Corporate Banking x2 https://bit.ly/4gidF3f\n- Intern - Customer Service Consultant x1 Phnom Penh https://bit.ly/4eYFPPZ\n\nDeadline: 15 July 2026\n \nHOW TO APPLY:\nInterested candidate may apply through the above link or scan QR code, or via email address:  jtrjobs@jtrustroyal.com', 'https://t.me/JTRBCareer/567', '/public/images/JTRBCareer/JTRBCareer_567.jpg', '2026-07-06 04:08:12', '2026-07-02 10:04:38'),
(253, 'Jobnetcambodia/1731', 'Jobnetcambodia', 'LagardГЁre Travel Retail бһҖбҹҶбһ–бһ»бһ„бһҸбҹ’бһҡбһјбһңбһҖбһ¶бһҡбһҮбҹ’бһҡбһҫбһҹбһҡбһҫбһҹбһ”бһ»бһӮбҹ’бһӮбһӣбһ·бһҖ Beauty Advisor (Techo Airport) бһұбһҖбһ¶бһҹбһҖбһ¶бһҡбһ„бһ¶бһҡбһ”бһ“бҹ’бһ‘бһ¶бһ”бҹӢбһҖбҹҶбһ–бһ»бһ„бһҡбһ„бҹӢбһ…бһ¶бҹҶбһўбҹ’бһ“бһҖбһ“бҹ…бһ‘бһёбһ“бҹҒбҹҮ бҹ” бһҖбһ»бҹҶбһІбҹ’бһҷбһұбһҖбһ¶бһҹбһҠбҹҸбһӣбҹ’бһўбһ“бҹҒбҹҮбһҖбһ“бҹ’бһӣбһ„бһ•бһ»бһҸбһ‘бҹ…\nбһҠбһ¶бһҖбҹӢбһ–бһ¶бһҖбҹ’бһҷбһҘбһЎбһјбһңбһ“бҹҒбҹҮ!\nhttps://www.jobnet.com.kh/job/beauty-advisor-techo-airport-lagardГЁre-travel-retail/5213\n\nLagardГЁre Travel Retail is looking to hire a Beauty Advisor (Techo Airport). Your next career opportunity is here. Don\'t miss out.\nApply now!\nhttps://www.jobnet.com.kh/job/beauty-advisor-techo-airport-lagardГЁre-travel-retail/5213', 'https://t.me/Jobnetcambodia/1731', '', '2026-07-06 04:08:12', '2026-06-26 03:51:37'),
