(606, 'CBjobopportunity/18299', 'CBjobopportunity', 'рҹ“ЈбһҠбҹҶбһҺбһ№бһ„бһҮбҹ’бһҡбһҫбһҹбһҡбһҫбһҹбһ”бһ»бһӮбҹ’бһӮбһӣбһ·бһҖбһ”бһ“бҹ’бһ‘бһ¶бһ“бҹӢ \n\nбһібһҖбһ¶бһҹбһҖбһ¶бһҡбһ„бһ¶бһҡбһ“бҹ… бһ•бһ¶бһ”бҹӢ(PUB) бһҠбҹӮбһӣбһҳбһ¶бһ“бһ‘бһёбһҸбһ¶бҹҶбһ„бһҹбҹ’бһҗбһ·бһҸбһ“бҹ…бһҖбҹ„бҹҮбһ“бһҡбһ¶ бһ“бһ·бһ„бһ‘бһ№бһҖбһҗбҹ’бһӣбһ¶ бһҡбһ¶бһҮбһ’бһ¶бһ“бһёбһ—бҹ’бһ“бҹҶбһ–бҹҒбһү\n\nрҹ“Ҙ бһҠбһ¶бһҖбҹӢбһ–бһ¶бһҖбҹ’бһҷбһҸбһ¶бһҳбһҡбһҷбҹҲ\nTelegram 070678078\n\nрҹ”ҺбһұбһҖбһ¶бһҹбһҖбһ¶бһҡбһ„бһ¶бһҡбһҗбҹ’бһҳбһёбҹ—\nTelegram Channel: https://t.me/CBjobopportunity\nChinese Job Channel: https://t.me/CamboJobchinese', 'https://t.me/CBjobopportunity/18299', '/public/images/CBjobopportunity/CBjobopportunity_18299.jpg', '2026-07-08 14:55:20', '2026-07-07 10:33:00'),
(607, 'CBjobopportunity/18300', 'CBjobopportunity', 'рҹ“ЈMidass Cambodia is urgently seeking for Provincial Sales Supervisor to join team.\n\nрҹ’° Salary: USD 850 вҖ“ 1,600/month (Base Salary + Allowances + Commission)\nвҸ° Working Hours: Minimum 8 hours/day, flexible based on business travel and field assignments.\nрҹҺҒ Benefits:\nвң”пёҸ Performance Bonus & Sales Commission\nвң”пёҸ Festival Benefits\nвң”пёҸ NSSF Insurance\nвң”пёҸ Career Growth Opportunities\nрҹ”Һ Requirements:\nвң”пёҸ Native Khmer speaker with strong communication skills\nвң”пёҸ Basic Chinese or English is a plus\nвң”пёҸ Minimum 2 years of sales experience in FMCG, food, or beverage industries\nвң”пёҸ Familiar with traditional trade, wholesale, retail, and modern trade channels\nвң”пёҸ High school diploma or above\nвң”пёҸ Age 25вҖ“40 (Male preferred)\nвң”пёҸ Valid motorcycle/car driving license\nвң”пёҸ Willing to travel frequently across provinces\n\nрҹ“Ҙ Apply Now:\nTelegram: @MidassHR\n\nрҹ‘ү Read Job Details: https://www.cambojob.com/jobs/jobs-show-22398-.htm', 'https://t.me/CBjobopportunity/18300', '/public/images/CBjobopportunity/CBjobopportunity_18300.jpg', '2026-07-08 14:55:20', '2026-07-07 11:00:39'),
(608, 'CBjobopportunity/18301', 'CBjobopportunity', 'рҹ“ЈCE Express is urgently seeking talented candidates to join our team.\n\nрҹ”Һ Open Positions\nвң”пёҸ Custom Clearance Manager (EN/CN)\nвң”пёҸ IT Product Specialist (CN) $480вҖ“$800\nвң”пёҸ Warehouse Clerk (CN) $300вҖ“$400\nвң”пёҸ Freight Customer Service (EN/CN) $300вҖ“$500\nвң”пёҸ Freight Operation Specialist (EN/CN) $300вҖ“$500\nвң”пёҸ Sales Specialist (Female, CN) $350вҖ“$500+Commission \n\nрҹ“Ҙ Apply Now:\nTelegram: @CE_HR_EXPRESS | @HRCEEXPRE\nвҳҺпёҸ 093370666 | 078444049 | 0717831800\nрҹ“§ Email: hr@cambodianexpress.com\n\nрҹ“Қlocation: Time Square 3, Street 335, Toul Kork, Phnom Penh', 'https://t.me/CBjobopportunity/18301', '/public/images/CBjobopportunity/CBjobopportunity_18301.jpg', '2026-07-08 14:55:20', '2026-07-08 03:03:54'),
(609, 'CBjobopportunity/18302', 'CBjobopportunity', 'рҹ“ЈбһҳбһҮбҹ’бһҲбһҳбһҺбҹ’бһҢбһӣбһҗбҹӮбһҹбһҳбҹ’бһ•бһҹбҹ’бһҹбһўбһ¶бһӣбһёбһҹ Alice Aesthetic CenterбһҖбҹҶбһ–бһ»бһ„бһҮбҹ’бһҡбһҫбһҹбһҡбһҫбһҹбһ”бһ»бһӮбҹ’бһӮбһӣбһ·бһҖ\n\nрҹ“ҘбһҠбһ¶бһҖбҹӢбһ–бһ¶бһҖбҹ’бһҷбһҘбһЎбһјбһңбһ“бҹҒбҹҮ!\nбһҸбҹҒбһӣбҹҒбһҖбҹ’бһҡбһ¶бһҳбҹ– @Suth_Thavrin \nрҹ“һбһӣбҹҒбһҒбһ‘бһјбһҡбһҹбҹҗбһ–бҹ’бһ‘бҹ– 01592296', 'https://t.me/CBjobopportunity/18302', '/public/images/CBjobopportunity/CBjobopportunity_18302.jpg', '2026-07-08 14:55:21', '2026-07-08 03:33:35'),
(610, 'CBjobopportunity/18303', 'CBjobopportunity', 'рҹ“ЈGolden Tower is urgently seeking talented candidates to join our team.\n\nрҹ”Һ Open Positionsпјҡ\n вң”пёҸAccounting Assistant  \n- Chinese Speaking 2pax\n-Chinese & Thai speaking 1pax \nвң”пёҸPersonal Assistant \n-Chinese Native Speakers/Foreigners\n\nвҸ° Working hours: \n8am вҖ“ 5:00pm (Mon-Sat)\n\nрҹ“ҘApply CV to: \nTelegram: 0887021732 / 070420494\nEmail: satchork20@gmail.com \n\nрҹ“ҚAddress: Golden Tower, No.158-166, St. 215, Sangkat Veal Vong, Khan 7 Makara, Phnom Penh', 'https://t.me/CBjobopportunity/18303', '/public/images/CBjobopportunity/CBjobopportunity_18303.jpg', '2026-07-08 14:55:21', '2026-07-08 04:02:38'),
