(615, 'CBjobopportunity/18308', 'CBjobopportunity', 'рҹ“ЈCHJ Jewellery Cambodia is urgently seeking Chinese-speaking, motivated, and talented individuals to grow with us!\n\nрҹ”Һ Open Positionsпјҡ\n вң”пёҸJewelry Sales ( Prefer Male / Chinese Speaking) \nрҹ“ҚAEON Mall 1\nрҹ“ҚAEON Mall 3\n вң”пёҸStore Manager (Chinese Speaking) \n\nрҹ“ҘApply CV to: \nEmail: satchork20@gmail.com \nTelegram: 0887021732 / 070420494', 'https://t.me/CBjobopportunity/18308', '/public/images/CBjobopportunity/CBjobopportunity_18308.jpg', '2026-07-08 14:55:21', '2026-07-08 08:05:12'),
(616, 'CBjobopportunity/18309', 'CBjobopportunity', 'рҹ“ЈбһұбһҖбһ¶бһҹбһҖбһ¶бһҡбһ„бһ¶бһҡ бһ“бҹ…бһҖбҹ’бһҡбһ»бһҳбһ бҹҠбһ»бһ“ HOMEWAY SUPPLY CHAIN CO., LTD\n\nбһҮбҹ’бһҡбһҫбһҹбһҡбһҫбһҹбһҹбһҳбҹ’бһҡбһ¶бһ”бҹӢ\nрҹ“Қбһ—бҹ’бһ“бҹҶбһ–бҹҒбһү бҹЎбһ“бһ¶бһҖбҹӢ\nрҹ“ҚбһҸбҹҶбһ”бһ“бҹӢбһҹбҹҒбһҠбҹ’бһӢбһҖбһ·бһ…бҹ’бһ…бһ–бһ·бһҹбҹҒбһҹбһҖбҹ’бһҡбһ»бһ„бһ–бҹ’бһҡбҹҮбһҹбһёбһ бһ“бһ» бҹЎбһ“бһ¶бһҖбҹӢ\n\nрҹ“Ҙ бһҠбһ¶бһҖбҹӢбһ–бһ¶бһҖбҹ’бһҷбһҸбһ¶бһҳбһҡбһҷбҹҲбҹ–\nвҳҺпёҸ 085 367 688\nTelegram: @hr_homeway\n\nрҹ‘ү бһ–бҹҗбһҸбҹҢбһҳбһ¶бһ“бһӣбһҳбҹ’бһўбһ·бһҸбҹ–\nhttps://www.cambojob.com/jobs/jobs-show-22276-.htm', 'https://t.me/CBjobopportunity/18309', '/public/images/CBjobopportunity/CBjobopportunity_18309.jpg', '2026-07-08 14:55:21', '2026-07-08 09:03:40'),
(617, 'CBjobopportunity/18310', 'CBjobopportunity', 'рҹ“Ј We are currently seeking a Pub Supervisor to join our team!\n\nрҹ”Һ Requirements:\nвң”пёҸ Male, under 35 years old\nвң”пёҸ At least 1 year of relevant experience\n\nрҹ•җ Working Hours:\n3:00 PM вҖ“ 12:00 AM\nрҹ“… 2 days off per week\n\nрҹҺҒ Benefits:\nвң… Khmer New Year & Pchum Ben holidays\n\nрҹ“Ҙ Apply Now\nTelegram: 0886820903\nTelegram: @hrvts', 'https://t.me/CBjobopportunity/18310', '/public/images/CBjobopportunity/CBjobopportunity_18310.jpg', '2026-07-08 14:55:21', '2026-07-08 09:33:20'),
(618, 'CBjobopportunity/18311', 'CBjobopportunity', 'рҹ“Ј AF Studio is Looking for Senior Architects and Junior Architects to Join Our Team!\n\nрҹ”Һ Requirements:\nвң”пёҸ Cambodian nationals with good English communication skills \nвң”пёҸ Bachelor\'s degree in Architectural Design \nвң”пёҸ Relevant industry experience is preferred\nвң”пёҸ Architectural Design Skills in protential design softwares are required \nSalary : From 400$ } Up to working experience \n\nвҸ° Working Hours:\nMonday вҖ“ Sunday | 8:30 AM вҖ“ 6:30 PM \nDay Off : 2 Days/ per month \n\nрҹ“Қ Work Location:\nAF Studio, Group 19 Village 2 District 4 Sihanoukville \n\nрҹ“Ҙ Apply Now:\nTelegram: t.me/Sovannalor\n\nрҹ‘үRead Job Details:', 'https://t.me/CBjobopportunity/18311', '/public/images/CBjobopportunity/CBjobopportunity_18311.jpg', '2026-07-08 14:55:22', '2026-07-08 10:00:14'),
(619, 'CBjobopportunity/18312', 'CBjobopportunity', 'рҹ“Ј AT DENT Clinic is urgently hiring!\nWe are looking for motivated and responsible candidates to join our professional dental team.\n\nрҹ•җ Working Hours:\n8:00 AM вҖ“ 5:15 PM\n\nWhat We Offer:\nвң”пёҸCompetitive salary\nвң”пёҸProfessional working environment\nвң”пёҸTraining and career growth\nвң”пёҸWork in a modern, high-end orthodontic clinic\nвң”пёҸContract: Minimum 2 years after passing 3 months probation period\n\nрҹ“Ҙ Apply now via\nTelegram: 098623736 (Ms. Pich)', 'https://t.me/CBjobopportunity/18312', '/public/images/CBjobopportunity/CBjobopportunity_18312.jpg', '2026-07-08 14:55:22', '2026-07-08 11:00:19'),
(620, 'CBjobopportunity/18313', 'CBjobopportunity', 'рҹ“Ј AT DENT Clinic is Urgently Hiring a General Dentist!\nWe are looking for motivated and responsible candidates to join our professional dental team.\n\nрҹ•җ Working Hours:\n8:00 AM вҖ“ 5:15 PM\n\nWhat We Offer:\nвң”пёҸCompetitive salary\nвң”пёҸProfessional working environment\nвң”пёҸTraining and career growth\nвң”пёҸWork in a modern, high-end orthodontic clinic\nвң”пёҸContract: Minimum 2 years after passing 3 months probation period\n\nрҹ“Ҙ Apply now via\nTelegram: 098623736 (Ms. Pich)', 'https://t.me/CBjobopportunity/18313', '/public/images/CBjobopportunity/CBjobopportunity_18313.jpg', '2026-07-08 14:55:22', '2026-07-08 11:33:35'),
(632, 'abacareers/2607', 'abacareers', 'Grow Your Career with ABA Bank! вңЁ\n\nWe are searching for talented and ambitious individuals to join us in growing their personal development and professional career for the following positions:\n\nрҹ’јPayment Solutions Specialistрҹ“ҚHead Office\nрҹҢҗApply Now:\nhttps://careers.ababank.com/jobs/mr1fpp3x_hu4ta\n\nрҹ’јSenior Card Acquisition and Merchant Partnership Consultantрҹ“ҚHead Office\nрҹҢҗApply Now:\nhttps://careers.ababank.com/jobs/mr39cvvpz_689q\n\nрҹ’јOutbound Sales Performance Management Specialistрҹ“ҚHead Office\nрҹҢҗApply Now:\nhttps://careers.ababank.com/jobs/ml0dt1asacf9kq\n\nрҹ‘ү Visit our ABA Careers website and create ABA Careers Profile here: careers.ababank.com\n\n#ABACareers #JoinABA #CareerOpportunity', 'https://t.me/abacareers/2607', '/public/images/abacareers/abacareers_2607.jpg', '2026-07-08 14:55:22', '2026-07-06 07:31:36'),
(633, 'abacareers/2608', 'abacareers', 'Grow Your Career with ABA Bank! вңЁ\n\nWe are searching for talented and ambitious individuals to join us in growing their personal development and professional career for the following positions:\n\nрҹ’јSmall Business Loan Traineeрҹ“ҚTboung Khmum Provincial Branch\nрҹҢҗApply Now:\nhttps://careers.ababank.com/jobs/mqz1x285dobxlq\n\nрҹ’јSmall Business Loan Traineeрҹ“ҚChaom Chau 2 branch\nрҹҢҗApply Now:\nhttps://careers.ababank.com/jobs/mr1f1nrqowduxg\n\nрҹ’јSmall Business Loan Traineeрҹ“ҚChbar Ampov Branch\nрҹҢҗApply Now:\nhttps://careers.ababank.com/jobs/mr1f3k8dmlp3fq\n\nрҹ’јSmall Business Loan Officer - Level 1рҹ“ҚOu Baek K Am Branch\nрҹҢҗApply Now:\nhttps://careers.ababank.com/jobs/mr1tpkw8ajhicq\n\nрҹ’јSmall Business Loan Officer - Level 1рҹ“ҚChaom Chau 2 branch\nрҹҢҗApply Now:\nhttps://careers.ababank.com/jobs/mr1ybnkufmuv9w\n\nрҹ’јSmall Business Loan Officer - Level 1рҹ“ҚBati District Branch\nрҹҢҗApply Now:\nhttps://careers.ababank.com/jobs/mr1yu4zgr25vcq\n\nрҹ‘ү Visit our ABA Careers website and create ABA Careers Profile here: careers.ababank.com\n\n#ABACareers #JoinABA #CareerOpportunity', 'https://t.me/abacareers/2608', '/public/images/abacareers/abacareers_2608.jpg', '2026-07-08 14:55:22', '2026-07-06 11:08:55'),
(634, 'abacareers/2609', 'abacareers', 'Grow Your Career with ABA Bank! вңЁ\nWe are searching for talented and ambitious individuals to join us in growing their personal development and professional career for the following positions:\n\nрҹ’јLoan Recovery Officerрҹ“ҚBanteay Meanchey Provincial Branch\nрҹҢҗApply Now:\nhttps://careers.ababank.com/jobs/mr1yo845xnefcg\n\nрҹ’јSmall Business Loan Officerрҹ“ҚKaoh Thum District Branch\nрҹҢҗApply Now:\nhttps://careers.ababank.com/jobs/mr1f5i7qb2n64g\n\nрҹ’јMedium Business Loan Officer - Level 1рҹ“ҚAngkor Chey District Branch\nрҹҢҗApply Now:\nhttps://careers.ababank.com/jobs/mr1yr0kbv1ssma\n\nрҹ’јMedium Business Loan Officer - Level 1рҹ“ҚChaom Chau 2 branch\nрҹҢҗApply Now:\nhttps://careers.ababank.com/jobs/mr3ailxxbcsefw\n\nрҹ’јSmall Business Loan Officer - Level 2рҹ“ҚStueng Trang District Branch\nрҹҢҗApply Now:\nhttps://careers.ababank.com/jobs/mr3ahavauzs5oa\n\nрҹ’јSmall Business Loan Supervisorрҹ“ҚCentral Branch\nрҹҢҗApply Now:\nhttps://careers.ababank.com/jobs/mr1z0ksnhafymw\n\n#ABACareers #JoinABA #CareerOpportunity', 'https://t.me/abacareers/2609', '/public/images/abacareers/abacareers_2609.jpg', '2026-07-08 14:55:23', '2026-07-07 02:35:20'),
(635, 'abacareers/2610', 'abacareers', 'рҹҢҠ рҹҸғрҹҸ»вҖҚвҷҖпёҸрҹҢ…бһҖбҹ’бһҡбҹ„бһҳбһ”бһҡбһ·бһҷбһ¶бһҖбһ¶бһҹбһҹбҹ’бһҡбһҹбҹӢбһҹбҹ’бһҡбһ¶бһҷбһ“бҹғбһҳбһ¶бһҸбҹӢбһҹбһҳбһ»бһ‘бҹ’бһҡ бһҖбҹ’бһҡбһ»бһҳбһҖбһ¶бһҡбһ„бһ¶бһҡбһ•бҹ’бһ“бҹӮбһҖбһ’бһ“бһ’бһ¶бһ“бһҳбһ“бһ»бһҹбҹ’бһҹ ABA бһ”бһ¶бһ“бһҡбһҪбһҳбһӮбҹ’бһ“бһ¶бһ…бһјбһӣбһҡбһҪбһҳбһҖбһҳбҹ’бһҳбһңбһ·бһ’бһё HR Sunrise Fun Run бһҠбҹӮбһӣбһҮбһ¶бһҹбһҖбһҳбҹ’бһҳбһ—бһ¶бһ–бһӣбһҫбһҖбһҖбһҳбҹ’бһ–бһҹбҹӢбһҹбһ»бһҒбһ»бһҳбһ¶бһӣбһ—бһ¶бһ– бһ”бһ„бҹ’бһҖбһҫбһ“бһҹбһ»бһҒбһ—бһ¶бһ–бһӣбҹ’бһў бһ“бһ·бһ„бһ–бһ„бҹ’бһҡбһ№бһ„бһҹбҹ’бһҳбһ¶бһҡбһҸбһёбһҖбҹ’бһҡбһ»бһҳбҹ”\nбһҡбһҸбҹӢбһҮбһ¶бһҳбһҪбһҷбһӮбҹ’бһ“бһ¶ бһ”бһ„бҹ’бһҖбһҫбһҸбһҹбҹ’бһ“бһ¶бһҳбһүбһүбһ№бһҳбһҮбһ¶бһҳбһҪбһҷбһӮбҹ’бһ“бһ¶ бһ“бһ·бһ„бһ”бһ“бҹ’бһҸбһҠбҹҶбһҺбһҫбһҡбһҶбҹ’бһ–бҹ„бҹҮбһ‘бҹ…бһҡбһҖбһ—бһ¶бһ–бһҮбҹ„бһӮбһҮбҹҗбһҷбһҮбһ¶бһҳбһҪбһҷбһӮбҹ’бһ“бһ¶! вңЁ\n\nрҹҢҠ рҹҸғрҹҸ»вҖҚвҷҖпёҸрҹҢ… Starting the day with the refreshing sea breeze and positive energy!\nThe ABA Human Resources team came together for the HR Sunrise Fun RunвҖ”a wellness activity that promotes employee well-being, encourages a healthy lifestyle, and strengthens team spirit.\nRunning together, sharing smiles, and moving forward toward success as one team! вңЁ\n\n#ABACareers #JoinABA #HRFunRun #TeamBuilding #HealthyTeam', 'https://t.me/abacareers/2610', '', '2026-07-08 14:55:23', NULL),
